@startuml seq-13-create-order
' 序列图13：创建订单
title 创建订单序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "product.js" as Front
participant "ProductController" as Ctrl
participant "ProductService" as Svc
participant "ProductMapper" as PMapper
participant "ProductOrderMapper" as OMapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 点击商品详情页"立即购买"
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/product/order/create(userId,productId,quantity)
Ctrl -> Svc: createOrder(userId,productId,quantity)
Svc -> PMapper: selectById(productId)
PMapper -> DB: SELECT * FROM product WHERE product_id=?
DB --> PMapper: Product
PMapper --> Svc: Product(含price)
Svc -> Svc: 计算total_price = price*quantity
Svc -> OMapper: insert(order)
OMapper -> DB: INSERT INTO product_order(status=0 待支付)
DB --> OMapper: order_id
OMapper --> Svc: order_id
Svc --> Ctrl: order_id
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, orderId}
Front --> User: 跳转订单页(待支付状态)

@enduml
